  "title": "docs(demo): add new example to illustrate the algolia ris tutorial",
  "body": "![demo-react](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6885378/21932915/41213c7e-d9a3-11e6-8d3d-2e187029e50b.gif)\r\n\r\nThis is the demo that will illustrate our React InstantSearch tutorial on the Algolia documentation website. \r\n\r\nSome comments:\r\n- I replaced the button that was clearing the facets and the query by our `<ClearAll/>` widget that only clear the facets. I added a note to discuss about adding another widget that will do both. Otherwise we should probably go for a connector here (but that's not that simple anymore).  \r\n- I used the `rc-slider` component for the range. It allowed me to have tooltip out of the box. ",
